## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.10+
- [`uv`](https://github.com/astral-sh/uv) installed:
  ```bash
  curl -Ls https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh
  ```

### Installation

Create a virtual environment and install dependencies:

```bash
uv sync
```

---

## ğŸ§ª Running Tests

```bash
uv run pytest
```

